fr.ecp.Group52_Project_IS1220_part1_AVEROUS_TOPUZ.Model.Network.Station

Class ParkingSlot

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.ecp.Group52_Project_IS1220_part1_AVEROUS_TOPUZ.Model.Network.Station.ParkingSlot
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    VisitableItems

    public class ParkingSlot
extends java.lang.Object
implements VisitableItems
    ParkingSlots is the class for all parking slots in the myVelib system. Every parking slot has a unique ID within the station it is built in. Its state defines if the parking slot is available or not. The state variable can take three values :
    • "free"
    • "taken"
    • "outOfOrder"
    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    Pierre Averous, Nicolas Topuz
